channel.description:
<big>:star: **Welcome to F11!** :star:</big>
Hosted by Geyde
### Rules
1. All standard forum rules apply, as usual. 2. Do not communicate about the game outside the game. 3. Do not attempt to angleshoot. 3. Please be respectful to your fellow players. Keep your salt in until post-game. 4. Don’t post in big text or otherwise pretend to be a host of this game. 5. Have fun.
### Mechanics
Days will be 48 hours long, or shorter if someone dies Nights will be 24 hours long Actions are done by submitting them through your class card or Mafia chat, and can be changed until the end of the night. Mafia chat is constant at all times. Lynches are [majority](https://wiki.mafiascum.net/index.php?title=Majority_Lynch) and [plurality](https://wiki.mafiascum.net/index.php?title=Plurality_voting) In order to vote, post `**/vote**`.
### Setup
One of the following role lists will be chosen at random.
* 1 Mafia Roleblocker, 1 Mafia Goon, 1 Cop, 1 Doctor, 5 Townies. * 1 Mafia Goon, 1 Mafia Roleblocker, 7 Townies. * 2 Mafia Goons, 1 Cop, 6 Townies. * 2 Mafia Goons, 1 Doctor, 6 Townies.
### Signups
If you want to join, reply to the OP with `**/in**` or `**/join**`
1. ~~Spoi~~ **Lynched D2** [color=green]**Townie**[/color] 2. WazzaAzza [color=green]**Townie**[/color] 3. ~~DatBird~~ **Lynched D3** [color=green]**Townie**[/color] 4. ~~MaximusPrime~~ **Killed N3** [color=green]**Doctor**[/color] 5. ~~Maxwell~~ **Lynched D4** [color=green]**Townie**[/color] 6. ~~an_gorta_pratai~~ **Lynched D1** [color=red]**Mafia Goon**[/color] 7. Eevee [color=red]**Mafia Goon**[/color] 8. ~~H_Hjasik~~ **Killed N1** [color=green]**Townie**[/color] 9. ~~Meteoro~~ **Killed N2** [color=green]**Townie**[/color]
### Thread Summary
[All potential rolecards posted](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/fm-f11-signups-9-9-rolling/75012/121)

item.title: [FM] F11! | Day 4 (3/9) | GAME END - eevee and an_gorta_pratai win!
item.dc:creator: Geyde
item.description:
I came into this worrying about how the game was going to turn out. Wondering if the extremely long time it took to fill would take a toll on the game’s activity.

Well, I was somewhat right.

As the first day went on I continually looked back at Eevee’s bastard game, of which has received significant attention. I look back to see an_gorta_pratai make a post about hardclaiming townie. It made me feel just a bit inadequate, like I did something horribly wrong. In reality I really had not, but it really hurt here. Even in the middle of my classes I kept checking back, praying that some, ANY deity would bestow legitimate activity upon the game. Sadly, my pleas were not answered in the slightest. I knew after seeing Maxi’s buddying to Eevee that there wasn’t going to be much way for town to win.

After a while, I just…gave up on the game. Didn’t put any effort into the flavor. Didn’t post VCs as often.

Sigh.

Is something wrong with me? Do people not like my games?

This is what I really thought as the game kept going, and it felt like shit.

Then F3 came along

I thought that it would be an easy time for Eevee to pull off the win in that situation given that he had been basically undisputed throughout the course of the entire game.

Watching it kind of reinvigorated my drive as host.

Wazza made some very good calls on eevee’s posts.
Maxwell kept a solid pro!town motivation the entire time.

It felt like a goddamn oasis in a desert.

Read full topic
